rget=\"_blank\"><\/a><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/arxiv.org\/abs\/2205.12329\" target=\"_blank\">2205.12329<\/a>\u00a0[astro-ph.HE].<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Big stars burn everything they have, die fast, and produce big black holes. So when you see two black holes together, it&#8217;s likely that the big black hole comes from the big star. Or maybe not? Before dying, the big &hellip; <a href=\"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/2022\/05\/25\/which-black-hole-formed-first-mass-ratio-reversal-in-massive-binary-stars-from-gravitational-wave-data\/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&rarr;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_coblocks_attr":"","_coblocks_dimensions":"","_coblocks_responsive_height":"","_coblocks_accordion_ie_support":"","_mi_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0},"categories":[5,11,15],"tags":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","amp_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4937"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4937"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4937\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":5316,"href":"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4937\/revisions\/5316"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4937"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/davidege